md:
giải nghĩa từ "listings" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan và các từ trái nghĩa.

* listing (noun)
	+ Meaning: a list of items or information
	+ Example: The real estate agent provided a listing of all the properties for sale in the area.
	+ Related words: catalog, directory, inventory
	+ Antonyms: none

* listing (verb)
	+ Meaning: to create a list of items or information
	+ Example: The company will list all the job openings on their website.
	+ Related words: catalog, record, register
	+ Antonyms: none

* listings (noun)
	+ Meaning: a collection of lists or information
	+ Example: The website provides listings of all the restaurants in the city.
	+ Related words: directory, catalog, database
	+ Antonyms: none

Note: The meanings and examples provided are based on the context of the word "listings" and may vary depending on the specific situation or industry.
